import math

def lcm_of_five_numbers(a, b, c, d, e):

    def lcm_two_numbers(x, y):
        gcd = math.gcd(x, y)
        return x * y / gcd
    lcm = lcm_two_numbers(a, b)
    lcm = lcm_two_numbers(lcm, c)
    lcm = lcm_two_numbers(lcm, d)
    lcm = lcm_two_numbers(lcm, e)
    return lcm
